\end{center}


\noindent\textbf{Environment notes}:
Python 3.x, NumPy/SciPy, and MNE for EEG preprocessing. Exact versions are
pinned in \texttt{requirements.txt}. Reproduction scripts verify file integrity at
startup by checking \texttt{SHA256SUMS.txt}.

The SHA-256 digest ledger ensures bitwise reproducibility of all code,
data, and figures covered in the archival snapshot, independent of
execution environment or platform.

